      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a basic set of wheels to get you from A to B? This vehicle is looking for a new home! While it has significant cosmetic wear and will require some mechanical attention to get it back to its best, it offers a great foundation for someone handy or looking for a value-priced entry into vehicle ownership. It's priced to reflect its current state and is ready for its next owner to take the reins!",
