    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable work car or a budget-friendly option for a daily commuter. While the engine and transmission remain functional, the exterior shows clear signs of age, including several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the roof's clear coat. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat bolster. It has been maintained regularly, though it will likely need some suspension work and new tires in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done but is no longer in its prime.",
