      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been consistently maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts exactly as it should, making it a dependable choice for daily driving. While there are some minor cosmetic blemishes consistent with its age, the interior is clean and all major systems are fully functional. You can expect a car that is ready for the road without any immediate repair needs.",
