    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute gem. Honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, and it's in truly pristine shape\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. It drives like a dream and has been kept meticulously clean. I'm sad to see it go, but I know it's going to make its next owner so happy. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
