      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available now is an exceptional E46 M3, a definitive benchmark in naturally aspirated performance. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen is mechanically superlative, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission with crisp, positive engagement. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, supported by a variable M differential lock and a perfectly tuned multi-link rear suspension. Every bushing, seal, and heat shield is in pristine order, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule with no deferred items. This is a collector-grade example of the ultimate driving machine.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
